Value: Marquee Resources Limited engages in the mineral exploration activities. The company holds a 100% interest in the Clayton Valley lithium project located in Nevada, the United States; a 100% interest in the Redlings REE project covering an area of 39.06 square kilometers located in Western Australia; the West Spargoville gold/nickel/lithium project covering an area of 80 square kilometers located in Western Australia; and a 100% interest in the Mt Clement project located in Western Australia. It also holds 30% interest in the Centenario lithium project located to the west of Salta City, Northern Argentina; and the Werner Lake cobalt projects located in Ontario, Canada. The company was incorporated in 2016 and is based in Subiaco, Australia.
